    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Discover the World: Explore City Treasures! Find Your Next Adventure</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            Welcome to Xplore - Your Collective Atlas of Urban Marvels! Share Your Discovered Gems, Unveil Untold
